msgid "State publication architecture"
msgstr "状态发布架构"

msgid "The standalone integration uses only a small Ray actor surface:"
msgstr "独立集成只使用很小的 Ray actor 接口面："

msgid ""
"A streaming `JobClient` registers its `JobManager` with one detached, zero-"
"CPU state actor on the Ray head node."
msgstr "流处理 `JobClient` 会把自己的 `JobManager` 注册到 Ray head 节点上一个分离、零 CPU 的状态 actor。"

msgid ""
"The state actor refreshes immutable snapshots concurrently and keeps the "
"last good snapshot for temporary actor outages and terminal history."
msgstr "状态 actor 会并发刷新不可变快照，并保留最近一次良好快照，以应对临时 actor 中断和终止作业历史。"

msgid ""
"`list_job_snapshots`, `get_job_snapshot`, `rescale_operator`, and "
"`cancel_job` expose a stable client API for CLIs, dashboards, and automation."
msgstr "`list_job_snapshots`、`get_job_snapshot`、`rescale_operator` 和 `cancel_job` 为 CLI、仪表板和自动化提供稳定客户端 API。"

msgid ""
"The bundled HTTP page is one adapter over this API. An eventual native Ray "
"Dashboard contribution can reuse the same boundary without moving scheduling "
"state into the dashboard process."
msgstr "内置 HTTP 页面是该 API 上的一个适配器。未来的原生 Ray Dashboard 贡献可以复用同一边界，无需将调度状态移入仪表板进程。"

msgid "\"Retained\" refers to the Ray actor identity, not to the Python operator object. A retained actor calls the operator's `build`/`open` lifecycle for a pending runtime while its old runtime is still open, then closes the old object in a supervised background cleanup after commit. Plain functions and Klein's framework operators support this handoff. Callable or lifecycle classes are rejected by default because constructors or `open()` may acquire exclusive external resources. Such a class may set `supports_concurrent_rescale = True` only when two task-local instances can safely overlap during rollback-preserving handoff."
msgstr "“保留”指的是 Ray Actor 的身份，而不是 Python 算子对象。保留的 Actor 会在旧运行时仍处于打开状态时，为待生效运行时调用算子的 `build`/`open` 生命周期；提交后，再通过受监督的后台清理关闭旧对象。普通函数和 Klein 框架算子支持这种切换。可调用类或生命周期类默认会被拒绝，因为其构造函数或 `open()` 可能获取独占外部资源。只有当两个任务本地实例能够在保留回滚能力的切换期间安全重叠时，此类才能设置 `supports_concurrent_rescale = True`。"

msgid "A stale or terminal job is read-only. Rescaling changes only the physical delta: subtasks whose indexes exist at both parallelisms retain their actor identities. On a scale-out, Klein creates the added actors and waits for them to answer a ping before it interrupts the data path. It then asks every direct upstream task to insert an ordered local barrier on the incident edge and pause at that cut. The target aligns those barriers, snapshots managed state, and fences its direct downstream tasks before Klein swaps routing and resumes the region. Unrelated actors stay alive; there is no whole-job restart or global source stop."
msgstr "过期或已终止的作业只能读取。扩缩容只改变物理差量：索引在新旧并行度中都存在的子任务会保留其 Actor 身份。扩容时，Klein 创建新增 Actor，并等待它们响应 ping 后才中断数据路径。随后，它要求每个直接上游任务在相连边上插入有序的局部屏障，并在该切面暂停。目标算子对齐这些屏障、快照托管状态并隔离其直接下游任务，然后 Klein 才切换路由并恢复该区域。无关 Actor 会继续存活；不会重启整个作业，也不会全局停止数据源。"

msgid "Added actors remain fenced while the local cut is formed. At the cut, retained actors prepare their new runtime descriptors and managed state transactionally, and added actors prepare their initial runtime and assigned state. The old runtime remains available until topology commit, so a pre-commit failure can roll back without changing the retained actor identities. On a scale-in, Klein does not create replacements: the removed actors stay fenced and available for rollback until commit, and only those removed actors are stopped afterward. With placement groups enabled, each physical actor owns an independently releasable single-bundle group. Scale-out reserves the added groups before the barrier, and scale-in releases the retired groups only after their actors stop. Retained actors and their reservations never move. This elastic layout trades job-wide gang scheduling and FORWARD-affinity bundle grouping for true incremental resource allocation and release. It accepts only `PACK` and `SPREAD`; `STRICT_PACK` and `STRICT_SPREAD` are rejected because separate actor groups cannot preserve a cross-actor strict-placement guarantee."
msgstr "形成局部切面期间，新增 Actor 始终处于隔离状态。在切面处，保留的 Actor 以事务方式准备新的运行时描述符和托管状态，新增 Actor 则准备初始运行时及分配给它们的状态。拓扑提交前旧运行时一直可用，因此提交前失败可以回滚，而不改变保留 Actor 的身份。缩容时 Klein 不创建替代 Actor：被移除的 Actor 在提交前保持隔离并可用于回滚，提交后才只停止这些 Actor。启用放置组后，每个物理 Actor 拥有一个可独立释放的单资源包组。扩容在屏障前预留新增组；缩容则在退役组的 Actor 停止后才释放这些组。保留的 Actor 及其预留资源始终不移动。这种弹性布局以作业级成组调度和 FORWARD 亲和资源包分组为代价，换取真正的增量资源分配与释放。它只接受 `PACK` 和 `SPREAD`；独立 Actor 组无法维持跨 Actor 的严格放置保证，因此会拒绝 `STRICT_PACK` 和 `STRICT_SPREAD`。"

msgid "Frontend contributors can run the source in `frontend/` and temporarily point 8266 at it with `--frontend-url`; production installations use the packaged UI."
msgstr "前端贡献者可以运行 `frontend/` 中的源码，并通过 `--frontend-url` 临时让 8266 端口指向该前端；生产安装使用已打包的 UI。"

msgid "If a source is itself a direct upstream of the target, that source task pauses cooperatively at a record boundary while the local cut is installed. Sources elsewhere in the graph keep running. Source operators cannot yet be the rescale target, and transactional or collecting sinks are also unsupported. Multiple source operators and parallel source subtasks are supported because the local cut pauses the target's direct upstream tasks rather than globally stopping every source. Unsupported API requests are rejected with the runtime-provided reason."
msgstr "如果某个数据源本身就是目标的直接上游，则在安装局部切面时，该源任务会在记录边界协作式暂停。图中其他位置的数据源继续运行。源算子目前不能作为扩缩容目标，事务型 Sink 和收集型 Sink 也不受支持。系统支持多个源算子和并行源子任务，因为局部切面暂停的是目标的直接上游任务，而不是全局停止所有数据源。不受支持的 API 请求会被拒绝，并返回运行时提供的原因。"

msgid "Klein listens on `127.0.0.1:8266` by default. The exact MUI/React Flow Klein UI is bundled in the `ray-klein` wheel, so serving it doesn't require a Ray source checkout, Node.js, port 3001, or changes to Ray Dashboard. Klein data and control requests stay on 8266. Overview, Jobs, Serve, Cluster, Actors, Metrics, Logs, and actor-detail links leave the gateway for the configured native Ray Dashboard. Set `RAY_KLEIN_RAY_DASHBOARD_URL`, or pass `--ray-dashboard-url`, when it uses a browser-visible proxy URL."
msgstr "Klein 默认监听 `127.0.0.1:8266`。完整的 MUI/React Flow Klein UI 已打包进 `ray-klein` wheel，因此提供该 UI 无需检出 Ray 源码、安装 Node.js、开放 3001 端口或修改 Ray Dashboard。Klein 的数据与控制请求都留在 8266 端口。Overview、Jobs、Serve、Cluster、Actors、Metrics、Logs 和 Actor 详情链接会离开该网关，转到已配置的原生 Ray Dashboard。如果该 Dashboard 使用浏览器可见的代理 URL，请设置 `RAY_KLEIN_RAY_DASHBOARD_URL` 或传入 `--ray-dashboard-url`。"

msgid "Start the standalone Klein Dashboard from a process connected to the Ray cluster:"
msgstr "从已连接 Ray 集群的进程启动独立 Klein Dashboard："

msgid "The normal scale path does not restart the job. Before the committed topology is released, the checkpoint coordinator arms every physical source in the target operator's physical `CheckpointDomain` set for one shared stabilization epoch. A checkpoint domain is a weakly connected component of physical execution edges, so independent FORWARD lanes and disconnected branches do not needlessly coordinate. Each selected source emits the same checkpoint ID at its next record or idle boundary. Barrier ordering forms the consistent cut, so sources keep producing while metadata becomes durable. Every task temporarily backpressures only a physical input channel whose barrier arrived early; other inputs keep draining until their matching barriers arrive, then the task snapshots and forwards the barrier once. Blocked records remain charged to the bounded inbox rather than moving to an unbounded side buffer; the finite set of in-flight control barriers has reserved admission so data traffic cannot starve alignment. The component's source offsets and operator shards are persisted atomically. Domains outside the target set do not join or wait for this epoch. The recovery fence is removed only after durability and source-state release. If any task fails after the local commit but before then, Klein deliberately falls back to a consistent global checkpoint recovery instead of restoring one task from stale state. If the coordinator is rebuilt during this window, Klein reclaims the old epoch and re-requests stabilization automatically."
msgstr "正常扩缩容路径不会重启作业。在释放已提交的拓扑前，检查点协调器会为目标算子的物理 `CheckpointDomain` 集合中的每个物理数据源启用同一个共享稳定化轮次。检查点域是物理执行边构成的弱连通分量，因此独立的 FORWARD 通道和不相连的分支无需进行多余协调。每个选中的数据源会在下一条记录或空闲边界发出相同的检查点 ID。屏障顺序形成一致性切面，因此数据源可以在元数据持久化期间继续生成数据。每个任务只会临时反压屏障提前到达的物理输入通道；其他输入继续排空，直到对应屏障到达，随后任务只执行一次快照并转发屏障。被阻塞的记录仍计入有界收件箱，而不会移入无界侧缓冲区；数量有限的在途控制屏障拥有预留准入能力，因此数据流量无法饿死对齐过程。该分量的数据源偏移量和算子分片会以原子方式持久化。目标集合之外的检查点域不会加入或等待此轮次。只有在持久化完成并释放源状态后，恢复隔离才会解除。如果任何任务在局部提交之后、解除前失败，Klein 会有意回退到一致的全局检查点恢复，而不是从陈旧状态恢复单个任务。如果协调器在此窗口内重建，Klein 会自动接管旧轮次并重新请求稳定化。"

msgid "The page also shows each operator's live parallelism and rates and exposes guarded local rescaling. Select an operator, enter the target parallelism in its details drawer, and confirm the change. When rescaling is unavailable, the disabled control shows the runtime-provided reason. The same operation remains available through the stable Python state API:"
msgstr "页面还会显示每个算子的实时并行度和速率，并提供带保护的局部扩缩容功能。选择一个算子，在其详情抽屉中输入目标并行度，然后确认变更。无法扩缩容时，禁用的控件会显示运行时给出的原因。同一操作也可通过稳定的 Python 状态 API 使用："

msgid "The page polls published job snapshots and renders the operator DAG. Like Flink's JobGraph, the whole node and its border continuously blend using the hottest subtask. Klein uses light cool-blue and warm-coral surfaces for idle and busy nodes, then blends toward amber for backpressure so dense metric text stays readable. Selecting a node or operator row opens a right-side drawer with subtask metrics. Separate views expose checkpoint history, per-operator state size, barrier alignment and latency, and redacted configuration."
msgstr "页面会轮询已发布的作业快照并渲染算子 DAG。与 Flink 的 JobGraph 类似，整个节点及其边框会根据最繁忙的子任务持续混合颜色。Klein 使用浅冷蓝和暖珊瑚色分别表示空闲与繁忙节点，并在发生反压时逐渐混合为琥珀色，使密集的指标文本仍然清晰可读。选择节点或算子行会打开右侧抽屉，显示子任务指标。独立视图还会展示检查点历史、各算子的状态大小、屏障对齐与延迟，以及经过脱敏的配置。"

msgid "The standalone Dashboard has no built-in authentication. Its default listener is loopback-only, and a non-loopback listener requires `--allow-unauthenticated`. Expose both Klein and Ray through the cluster's authenticated operations proxy."
msgstr "独立 Dashboard 不内置身份认证。它默认只监听回环地址；监听非回环地址必须使用 `--allow-unauthenticated`。请通过集群已认证的运维代理同时对外提供 Klein 和 Ray。"
